1. **NO TIMESTAMPED DOCS** тАФ NEVER create files like `*_2026-03-*.md`, `*AUDIT_2026*.md`, `*REPORT_2026*.md`
2. **UPDATE SSOT, DON'T CREATE** тАФ Audits/diagnostics/reports MUST update `AGENTS.md`, `TASKS.md`, or `docs/SYSTEM_MAP.md`, not create new files
3. **HANDOFFS ARE EPHEMERAL** тАФ Consolidate learnings in `docs/knowledge/HARVEST.md` and archive handoffs >30 days to `docs/_archived_handoffs/YYYY-MM/`
