## CONTEXT TRACKER (MANDATORY)

> Every session carries a **CTX score** (0тАУ280). When CTX тЙе 180 the agent MUST warn. When CTX тЙе 250 the agent MUST run `/end` autonomously.

| Zone | CTX | Action |
|------|-----|--------|
| ЁЯЯв SAFE | 0тАУ100 | Continue normally |
| ЁЯЯб WARN | 101тАУ180 | Wrap up subtask, plan /end |
| ЁЯФ┤ HIGH | 181тАУ250 | Start /end soon тАФ commit + handoff |
| тЫФ CRITICAL | 251тАУ280 | Execute /end NOW, then ask user to open new chat |

- **Agent:** `bun agent:run context_tracker --dry` тАФ run anytime, mandatory before long multi-step tasks
- **Auto-trigger rule:** If the agent detects CTX тЙе 250 it MUST emit `/end` without waiting for user prompt
- **Score factors:** uncommitted files ├Ч 4, session commits ├Ч 2, changed code files ├Ч 1, handoff size (KB) ├Ч 0.5, agent runs ├Ч 8

